    "subject": "1girl, solo, stunning young asian woman, k-pop idol aesthetic, ulzzang face, cute and alluring, soft v-shape face, pale porcelain skin, natural makeup with blush",
    "hair": "long platinum white hair, see-through bangs (air bangs), messy hair strands, wind blown, silky texture, floating hair",
    "eyes": "large crystal blue eyes, watery eyes, wearing contact lenses, long eyelashes, looking at viewer with innocent gaze",
    "expression_action": "mouth closed, soft smile, head slightly tilted, relaxed shoulders, standing naturally, charming aura",
    "outfit": "grey ribbed knit camisole, tight fitting, showcasing curves, grey skater skirt, high waist, texture of knitted fabric clearly visible",
    "environment": "blurred park background, soft greenery, creamy bokeh, daylight, airy atmosphere",
    "technical": "masterpiece, best quality, 8k, photorealistic but with soft focus aesthetic, cinematic lighting, soft diffusion, f/1.8, 85mm lens, detailed skin texture without being harsh"
  },
  "negative_prompt": "holding hands, covering mouth, hand on face, western features, mature face, harsh shadows, strong contrast, low quality, worst quality, bad anatomy, extra fingers, cartoon, sketch, deep shadows, oily skin, shiny skin, plastic looking",
  "final_prompt_string": "A stunningly beautiful young Asian woman with a K-pop idol aesthetic, featuring a soft V-shaped face and pale porcelain skin. She has long, platinum white hair with airy see-through bangs and loose, wind-blown strands creating a natural messy look. Her eyes are large, crystal blue (resembling contact lenses), looking directly at the viewer with a pure and innocent expression. She is wearing a tight-fitting grey ribbed knit camisole that highlights her figure, paired with a matching grey skater skirt. The background is a soft, out-of-focus park scene with creamy bokeh. The lighting is diffused and airy, creating a dreamy, soft-focus photorealistic portrait, 8k resolution, detailed texture."
}

